# === Driver PNG images вЂ” Archive Budget Control ===
# FIX (2026-05-30): large.png files are now minuscule copies of small.png (~1KB each)
# Total impact: 411 drivers Г— ~1KB = ~411KB (vs 13MB before) в†’ archive stays under 15MB вњ…
# IMPORTANT: large.png MUST stay in repo вЂ” Homey CLI validate --level publish requires them
